{
  "stem": "10181.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And she figured that she would go to England and we would come whenever things were-- whenever she would settle down and she could bring us over.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Holland was neutral after all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And if there's going to be a war, nothing would happen to us in Holland.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "This was her consideration.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "On September 1, she came to visit us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And instead of staying a week, she-- she-- the same day she went she left because my uncle said to her that he just heard on the news that the Germans had invaded Poland.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And he said, there's gonna be a war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And they're going to stop passenger ships, so you better leave.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So she managed to get the last ship, passenger ship, from Holland to England.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] Holland is sort of a little-- little harbor, which from there you take ships to England.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "In those days, you didn't fly.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "You took a ship.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And this-- I didn't know at the time that it was the last ship, that I found out after the war.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But even then, I was disappointed that she only stayed for one day.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But it-- you know, it didn't bother me that much.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "I thought, OK, another few months, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "You know, in the meanwhile, I'm having a good time here.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I'm going to school.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "I make friends.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Not so-- not so terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Life wasn't-- wasn't that terrible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And the war did start, but it didn't affect us very much, at least us kids didn't affect us very much.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because like I said, Holland at the beginning was neutral.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And we continued to go to school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And the Nazis were active, but they were the minority.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They were-- they-- they were vocal, but they were the minority.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "They were not in the government.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
